{"id":153405,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/土耳其人举行反网络审查示威游行/","date":"2011-05-19T20:22:09Z","modified":"2011-09-27T17:15:48Z","title":"土耳其人举行反网络审查示威游行","content":"<p>上周日，数以千计的土耳其居民涌上伊斯坦布尔街头，抗议政府审查互联网。 Haberturk媒体声称伊斯坦布尔塔克斯木广场聚集了5万民众，CNN称土耳其全国的示威者数以十万。土耳其政府将在8月22日开始实施新的互联网管理制度，要求ISP提供四个过滤选项：家庭，儿童，国内和标准。许多网站预计将因此被屏蔽。抗议者设立了名为“Internetime Dokunma!（意思是不要动我的互联网）”的Facebook活动页面，有超过60万人加入。抗议者指责土耳其政府屏蔽了6万个网站。<img src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14e65a13/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%BE%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%8D%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B8%B8%E8%A1%8C&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F17%2F052252%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%BE%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%8D%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B8%B8%E8%A1%8C&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F17%2F052252%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092569910/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14e65a13/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092569910/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14e65a13/a2.img\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=wq61mgOZalM:JF4gCR-LCVM:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=wq61mgOZalM:JF4gCR-LCVM:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><i